<p class="ql-align-center">不远处的黑虎泉边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看“清泉石上流”，听叮咚的泉水声，胜似江南</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/7cd1dbda89fe432b822b1d927ede58f5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
